**Step 3: Expand $(1-y)^2$**

$(1-y)^2 = 1 - 2y + y^2$

$$\int_0^{0.4} 60 y^3(1 - 2y + y^2) dy = \int_0^{0.4} 60(y^3 - 2y^4 + y^5) dy$$

