- $y^6 = (0.4)^6 = 0.004096$

$$= 60\left[\frac{0.0256}{4} - \frac{2(0.01024)}{5} + \frac{0.004096}{6}\right]$$

$$= 60\left[0.0064 - 0.004096 + 0.000682667\right]$$

$$= 60\left[0.002686667\right]$$

$$= 0.161200$$

